Both the **knowledge pipeline** (upload, ingestion, analysis, feedback — 22 entry points) and the **unit generation pipeline** (wizard, all generation routes, import, admin test sandbox — 20 entry points) have been **quarantined**. All API routes return HTTP 410 Gone. All UI entry points disabled. Full register: `docs/quarantine.md`. Grep marker: `QUARANTINED (3 Apr 2026)`.

